episodes.title: BoJack Horseman: The BoJack Horseman Story, Chapter One
episodes.plot: A publishing house eagerly awaits BoJack's memoirs, but he hasn't even started yet. His agent/ex and his publisher try to talk him into working with a ghost writer, but BoJack's too despondent about being washed up to focus.

episodes.title: BoJack Hates the Troops
episodes.plot: BoJack gets into trouble after taking muffins a Navy Seal had "dibs" on and then calling American soldiers jerks on live television.

episodes.title: Prickly Muffin
episodes.plot: A child actress from the sitcom BoJack starred in 20 years ago shows up at his house leading to a series of chaotic events.

episodes.title: Zoës and Zeldas
episodes.plot: Bojack mentors Todd in his upcoming career; meanwhile Diane's ex-boyfriend writes an article about Mr. Peanutbutter for an online article.

episodes.title: Live Fast, Diane Nguyen
episodes.plot: A business trip for BoJack and Diane takes a detour; Todd runs a scam that gets him in trouble.

episodes.title: Our A-Story Is a 'D' Story
episodes.plot: In a bout of drunken jealousy toward Mr. Peanutbutter, BoJack steals the "D" from the Hollywood sign for Diane. Meanwhile, Todd finds himself juggling two very demanding dates.

episodes.title: Say Anything
episodes.plot: Princess Carolyn tries to have it all and prove she's the best agent in the biz, while Bojack, Todd, and Vanessa Gecko make it as difficult as possible.

episodes.title: The Telescope
episodes.plot: When he learns his old friend from "Horsin' Around" is dying, BoJack tries to mend fences.

episodes.title: Horse Majeure
episodes.plot: A love struck BoJack tries to sabotage a wedding; Todd accepts a surprising new professional role.

episodes.title: One Trick Pony
episodes.plot: BoJack shoots a movie at Mr. Peanutbutter's house; Diane finishes her book.

episodes.title: Downer Ending
episodes.plot: BoJack embarks on a project in his typically gonzo style, leading to a drug-fueled revelation.

episodes.title: Later
episodes.plot: Months after his memoir is released, BoJack's being considered for a role that's a life long dream.
